# Skill: Projects - Quan ly Du an

## Muc dich
Skill nay giup doc docs va code nhanh cho module Projects

## Workflow 5 Buoc

### Buoc 1: Thu thap thong tin
- Xac dinh yeu cau tu user (CRUD, report, feature moi)
- Neu thieu thong tin, hoi user cung cap chi tiet
- Validate input dau vao

### Buoc 2: Tim kiem va Phan tich
- Doc file `docs/projects.md` de hieu ro module
- Kiem tra `CODE_BASE_HE_THONG.md` de nam tong quan
- Tim files lien quan (Models, Controllers, Components, Services)
- Xac dinh pham vi cong viec

### Buoc 3: Lap ke hoach
- Tom tat ngan gon nhung gi se lam
- Liet ke cac files se sua doi
- Xac dinh cac rang buoc va quy uoc can tuan thu

### Buoc 4: Thuc thi
- Thuc hien cong viec theo ke hoach
- Tuan thu conventions trong `CLAUDE.md` va `GIT_RULES_WORKFLOWS.md`
- Khong mo rong scope ngoai yeu cau neu chua co xac nhan

### Buoc 5: Bao cao va Hoan tat
- Bao cao tien do sau moi moc chinh
- Khi hoan tat, liet ke:
  - File da sua doi
  - Test/lint da chay (neu co)
  - Cap nhat task list
- Chay skill `init-he-thong.skill` de cap nhat `CODE_BASE_HE_THONG.md`
- Cap nhat file skill nay neu co thay doi ve files lien quan

## Files lien quan
### Backend
- Models: backend/app/Models/Project.php, ProjectProcedure.php, ProjectProcedureRaci.php, ProjectProcedureStep.php
- Controllers: backend/app/Http/Controllers/ProjectController.php
- Routes: backend/routes/api.php
- Services: backend/app/Services/V5/Domain/ProjectDomainService.php, backend/app/Services/V5/ProjectProcedure/*.php

### Frontend
- Components: frontend/components/ProjectList.tsx, ProjectProcedureModal.tsx, ProcedureTemplateManagement.tsx, RaciMatrixPanel.tsx, ProjectRevenueSchedulePanel.tsx
- Services: frontend/services/v5Api.ts
- Types: frontend/types.ts

### Docs
- `docs/projects.md` - Tai lieu chi tiet module

## Permissions
- projects.read, projects.write, projects.delete
- projects.import, projects.export

## Tab ID
- projects

## Tham chieu
- `CLAUDE.md` - Project conventions
- `GIT_RULES_WORKFLOWS.md` - Git workflow
- `init-he-thong.skill` - Setup guide
- `CODE_BASE_HE_THONG.md` - Codebase overview
